{
  "stem": "10572.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I took him to the church services of Camp Ashby.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he sat there and he says, I don't believe this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, what do you mean?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said how did this happen?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, you know, Pastor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, yeah, i know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said 2,000 years ago, another Jew tried to teach you what later on became Christianity.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's all I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And ultimately I was transferred out of Camp Ashby and transferred to Third Service Command headquarters in Baltimore into counterintelligence.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we formed a team of five agents who somehow had a little bit of the same background as I had.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had one fellow from Holland, a Jewish boy from Holland, and others who were trained and trained to become interrogators and do political classification of prisoners, and that-- do political classification so that AMG, Allied Military Government, could use our classification done in the place of an American POW camp for reconstruction of Germany.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After they were being sent back, our classification sheets were part of their personnel file.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was an unbelievable, fascinating work that we did for a couple of years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had 300,000 prisoners of war in America, and many of them in the Third Service Command that we classified.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And at the same time, we did war crime investigation as we ran across things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I found a guy who, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who was in the SS-- SS Hohenstaufen who, during the Battle of the Bulge, had captured-- his outfit had captured members of the 101st Airborne Division.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he participated in the killing of 25 of enlisted men of 101st Airborne Division.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, those things didn't just come to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It happened that one day, a prisoner of war who was an anti-Nazi came to me and told me that while he was in Oxford, England in a prisoner of war camp, this man Fritz Zilke had bragged about the fact that he had participated in this killing.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was all he knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I had Fritz Zilke transferred from this camp in Virginia to Maryland, where I interrogated him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was in the camp where there were many other SS men there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he didn't know what I was-- he pretended he didn't know what I was talking about.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had to use my CIC technique that we had learned.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I told him that he didn't have to tell me anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All I would do is turn him over to the SS in the camp, and tell them what he had told me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they would take care of him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he knew that was true.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So little by little, he started to give.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And little by little, this whole case developed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he showed me pictures of the commanding officer who had given the orders to kill the 25 101st Airborne Division men.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we took, took depositions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the depositions then were put in the regular legal form.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we had a man that came in-- one of our members-- CIC members who was an FBI agent in civilian life before he came in the army--",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Counterintelligence corps.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we have this, regular deposition, with question and answer, so that ultimately this deposition could be used to sentence him as a war criminal.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that went with his file.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then there were the [INAUDIBLE] that I had in Fort Meade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The intelligence officer was a man who was a very tough guy, big Irishman who was in the 101st Airborne Division, had been wounded, sent back, and was now the intelligence officer in the prisoner of war camp in Fort Meade, Maryland.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day, he called me-- no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One day, after we took these depositions from Zilke, Zilke came to me one day and he said that some of the people in the camp had threatened him that he had turned a traitor because he was called out and called out.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said to Captain Baker, who was the commanding officer of this little camp-- and I said, transfer him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Transfer him to Fort Meade, so that we don't have a killing here which you have to investigate.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he had him transferred to Fort Meade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had no thought-- didn't think of Major Erwin, I think, was his name-- that he was in Fort Meade.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I got a call from him at headquarters one day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Erwin, who had become a good buddy of mine, called me and said, my gosh.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, you almost got me court-martialed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, what happened?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, you sent that little bastard in.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
